reviews.review_text: Why pick on Billy K? wow, seems like a cool show and a rather good recording with Beyer M88 mics,  but why the Billy K news article ?  Please take it down ... it's not cool, I've never seen anything like this on ANY music download/streaming site ... Journalism SUCKS today and we don't need it HERE ... DL
